            <title><![CDATA[【容易感染！#千万不要用牙咬倒刺#[揣手]】医生提醒，口水里含有细菌，用牙齿去咬可能会导致继发感染！处理倒刺牢记这三步👇🏻✅处理倒刺前先拿温水进行软化...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【容易感染！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E7%89%99%E5%92%AC%E5%80%92%E5%88%BA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E7%94%A8%E7%89%99%E5%92%AC%E5%80%92%E5%88%BA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#千万不要用牙咬倒刺#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[揣手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/af/2022_chuaishou_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<br><br>医生提醒，口水里含有细菌，用牙齿去咬可能会导致继发感染！处理倒刺牢记这三步👇🏻<br><br>✅处理倒刺前先拿温水进行软化；<br>✅用指甲剪在根部将倒刺剪掉；<br>✅剪掉倒刺后涂抹润肤剂，促进皮肤修复。<br><br>问题来了，发现倒刺你是怎么处理的？<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hibblyas4pg20es0boquh.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
